              </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="works__box-item">
              <div class="works__box-pic">
                <img src={`${baseUrl}/images/works_persol.png`} alt="" />
              </div>
              <ul class="works__box-content">
                <li class="works__box-items">
                  <span>Client</span>
                  <p>パーソルメディアスイッチ株式会社</p>
                </li>
                <li class="works__box-items">
                  <span>Project</span>
                  <p>企業ミッション</p>
                </li>
                <li class="works__box-items">
                  <span>Type</span>
                  <div class="works__box-type">
                    <span>Editorial</span>
                    <span>Copywriting</span>
