            <p class="cta__text">お客さまの抱える課題、悩みに合わせた最適なソリューションをご提案いたします。 まずはお気軽にご相談ください。</p>
            <p class="cta__text-sub">We will propose optimal solutions tailored to the issues and problems you face. Please feel free to contact us for a consultation.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="#" class="cta__button">
            <span>お問い合わせ</span>
            <div class="cta__arrow">
              <span class="cta__arrow-arrow">(</span>
              <span class="cta__arrow-arrow">)</span>
            </div>
          </a>
